data.title: Bumper – A Day in the Life of a Titan
data.description: Sangbeom “Bumper” Park has found himself the vocal and emotional leader of the flawless Vancouver Titans. Follow Bumper as he prepares for a match day and discusses his innate ability to lead his team to victory day in and day out.

data.title: The Moms of the Overwatch League
data.description: We invited 5 moms of Overwatch League pros to the Blizzard Arena to hear what their sons had to say about the love and support they’ve received throughout their esports careers. Find out what it means to be one of the #OWLMoms.

A Perfect Stage for the San Francisco Shock?
data.description: The San Francisco Shock have the opportunity to go a perfect stage, not dropping a single map in 24 maps played. Sinatraa and Rascal sound off on their success and Sinatraa reveals his “dirty secret” that may lead to their victories.

data.title: Defined: Pocket
data.description: What does it mean to "pocket" another player? Hear from San Francisco Shock's Super, Houston Outlaws' Rawkus, and Philadelphia Fusion's EQO explain how a little extra help can help a player pop off! It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Learn more at http://www.Intel.com/OWL

data.title: My Hero: Lúcio
data.description: In this episode of My Hero, learn why Lúcio's been such an important hero for OWL teams and how you can make the best of this fast, slippery hero from Los Angeles Valiant's Custa and Philadelphia Fusion's Neptuno. It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel.

Shanghai Dragons Break Through to Their First Stage Playoffs
data.description: It’s no secret that the Shanghai Dragons struggled to find momentum during the Inaugural Season of the Overwatch League. With star DPS players DDing and Diem now leading the charge, Shanghai talks about qualifying for the Stage 2 playoffs and the road ahead.

data.title: Atlanta’s Reign over New York
data.description: Do you believe in miracles? Dogman and BabyBay walk through the moments when they managed to take down the juggernauts of the New York Excelsior.

data.title: Meta Report: Stage 2
data.description: In Stage 2, the triple-tank triple-support "GOATS" meta has expanded! In this episode of the Meta Report, learn how heroes like Winston, Ana, Sombra, and Baptiste have made their way into 3-3 comps! It's all part of Insights: powered by Intel. Learn more at http://www.Intel.com/OWL

data.title: Dallas is Fueled Up for Homestand Weekend
data.description: After playing in Los Angeles for nearly two seasons, the Dallas Fuel are ready to kick off the first Overwatch League Homestand Weekend and welcome all the other teams to their turf! OGE and Note discuss to what they are most looking forward.
